NEO4JAWS (Pronounced Neo Four Jaws)
-----------------------------------

Gradle and Chef recipes for bootstrapping a Neo4J instance on Amazon Web Services


With Thanks
-----------

Much of this code was inspired by the sample build by Jeppe Nejsum Madsen. 

The original article series and github source are available here:  

* https://github.com/jeppenejsum/helloworld
* http://jeppenejsum.wordpress.com/2009/05/03/ec2-continuous-deployment-hello-world/ 